Kairana stands as a Lok Sabha constituency with a rich political legacy,

Kairana is one of the Lok Sabha seats of Uttar Pradesh. Kairana situated in western Uttar Pradesh, stands as a Lok Sabha constituency with a rich political legacy. Encompassing portions of Saharanpur and Shamli districts, this seat boasts a diverse political landscape characterized by the presence of prominent parties such as the BJP, RLD, SP and INC.

Kairana Lok Sabha Election Result 2024

The polling for Kairana was held in Phase 1 on 19 April. The key candidates for the 2024 General Elections in Kairana are Pradeep Kumar contesting from BJP and Iqra Choudhary of Samajwadi Party (SP). As per the latest trends of counting of votes for 2024 Lok Sabha elections, BJP’s Pradeep Kumar is leading this Kairana seat.

In the 2019 Lok Sabha elections, the Kairana seat was won by BJP candidate Pradeep Kumar, while SP candidate Tabassum Begum had come in second place. In 2014’s General Elections, Kairana constituency was won by BJP candidate Hukum Singh and SP candidate Nahid Hasan was the runner-up.
